description:
This is a market on whether the democratic or republican candidate will win the U.S. Senate runoff in Georgia taking place on January 5th, 2021. Currently, candidates for this election are David Perdue on the Republican ticket, and Jon Ossoff on the Democratic ticket. The linked PredictIt question is the basis for the creation of this market and will be referenced as the leading resolution source, https://www.predictit.org/markets/detail/6651/Which-party-wins-the-regularly-scheduled-2020-US-Senate-election-in-Georgia. This market will resolve when the PredictIt market is resolved, to the same outcome.

Disclaimer: Likely candidates for each party are listed in the outcome names for clarity, however, if for whatever reason the candidates change, this market will be resolved based on the party the winning candidate associates with.
